graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    KServe -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes 1.28+<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    KServe -->|serverless autoscaling| Knative[Knative Serving 0.44.0<br/>Optional - Serverless Mode]
    KServe -->|traffic routing, mTLS| Istio[Istio 1.24+<br/>Optional - Service Mesh]
    KServe -->|event-driven autoscaling| KEDA[KEDA 2.16+<br/>Optional - Raw Deployments]
    KServe -->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager Latest<br/>Optional - Alt: OpenShift CA]
    KServe -->|modern ingress| GatewayAPI[Gateway API 1.2.1<br/>Optional - Alt: Istio VS]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    KServe -.->|service mesh| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh Istio<br/>VirtualService, DestinationRule]
    KServe -->|model metadata| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>gRPC/REST API]
    KServe -->|token validation| Authorino[Authorino<br/>AuthorizationPolicy]
    KServe -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>REST API]
    KServe -.->|auth tokens| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>ServiceAccount Tokens]

    %% Integration Points
    DSP[Data Science Pipelines] -->|auto deploy models| KServe
    DashboardUI[ODH Dashboard UI] -->|lifecycle mgmt| KServe
    KServe -->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>ServiceMonitor CRD]
    KServe -->|traces/metrics| OpenTelemetry[OpenTelemetry<br/>OpenTelemetryCollector CRD]

    %% External Services
    KServe -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO/Ceph]
    KServe -->|model storage| GCS[GCS Storage<br/>Google Cloud]
    KServe -->|container images| ContainerRegistry[Container Registries<br/>Quay/Docker Hub/ECR]
    KServe -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>CRD reconciliation]

